make sure telnet is installed
make sure telnet-server or telentd is installed
check if xinetd is installed, if not then execute
sudo apt-get install xinetd

set disable = no in all the following
/etc/xinetd.d/chargen
/etc/xinetd.d/daytime
/etc/xinetd.d/discard
/etc/xinetd.d/echo
/etc/xinetd.d/time

run command 
sudo /etc/init.d/xinetd restart